.TH XIL\-SAMPLE "1" "2026\-04\-05" "xil\-pipeline 0.1.3" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
xil\-sample
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B xil\-sample
[-h] (--episode TAG | --cast PATH) [--show SHOW] [--dry-run] [--force]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Generate a voice sample MP3 for each assigned cast member.

.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-episode\fR \fI\,TAG\/\fR
Episode tag (e.g. S02E03); derives cast config path

.TP
\fB\-\-cast\fR \fI\,PATH\/\fR
Explicit path to cast JSON file

.TP
\fB\-\-show\fR \fI\,SHOW\/\fR
Show name override (default: from project.json)

.TP
\fB\-\-dry\-run\fR
Print what would be generated without calling the API

.TP
\fB\-\-force\fR
Regenerate samples even if files already exist on disk

